column5: Was able to take part in the windy city redneck podcast last week. If anyone has a long drive or is bored and has time to kill, might be a decent listen. Here's the link;https://open.spotify.com/episode/7oZ...TNq8HrZK7EdEew
Thanks for sharing - rreally enjoyed that! If I am ever in Chicago I am going to make sure I check out Horse Thief Hollow Andrew
Send me a message before and I'll buy ya a beer! Glad you enjoyed!
